{"tid":1589562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要·正視聽］唔好再講警察「拉人拘捕人」，佢地係綁架人！","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:06:03.000Z","uid":321749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1a739557710183e6d89a0d484de2efff3018cd","tid":1589562,"uid":321749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"續上個post<br />\n外國朋友覺得奇怪，明明已經當警察做黑社會，但點解香港人仲話警察「拉人」「拘捕人」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574656</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n班黑警唔洗3個月已經顛晒，或者應該話露出晒真面目，完美演繹咩係濫權濫捕<br />\n<br />\n買雷射觀星筆，捉！<br />\n和平遊行，捉！<br />\n和平唱歌仔，捉！<br />\n生得後生d靚d，捉！<br />\n講句跌左良心，捉！<br />\n10歲小朋友講句口嘅，捉！<br />\n帶3張八達通，捉！<br />\n出街帶藥物，捉！<br />\n<br />\n仲有大把濫捕既cases呀！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢d完完全全就係恐怖分子既綁架！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該以後無論現場、口傳、文字、文宣、民間記招等，都唔好再話佢地拉人捉人拘捕人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n先唔好理有無用，但佢地做緊既野就係綁架，講番事實！<br />\n<br />\n而且根據marketing 既anchoring effect 錨定效應，大眾久而久之就會質疑佢地係行使警權定真係綁架！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要令大眾否定佢地既權力呀！佢地唔再有合法權力呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以後記住：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警綁架市民！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警綁架市民！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警綁架市民！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"515728835f6f936c47bf82f237d1754bee2fc326","tid":1589562,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":